Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…要遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經放暑假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊呀 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 不要搗蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都說不行了啦 很癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前略 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不肖頑弟上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自暑假初始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已然大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}尚存理性與否
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無自知矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在！怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這攝影機是買的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那看起來還真是古舊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在家裡的倉庫找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想…大概是逝世的爺爺留下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知怎的…挺中意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶吶 該怎麼用啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裝上這卷膠卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後對好鏡頭的焦距
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後按下快門就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從暑假的第一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就變得「坦率」多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才…才沒那種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在幹嘛呢 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在練柔韌性吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 讓我們開始快快樂樂的電影製作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天要拍什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}負責劇本的是檸檬學姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的份已經寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的份？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的拍片風格是香港式的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一天要拍的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那天的早上決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不是到哪兒說哪兒嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}換好衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好棒！很合適啊 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這衣服是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來好像斥資不菲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我拜託學校的COSPLAY社團和我們合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們還有這種社團嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會不會很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.11,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}女主人公降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.11,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}與少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.11,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}相遇 然後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天要拍的內容是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角第一次與那個男孩相遇的場景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}言情劇啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不好很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順帶一提 女主角的設定是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真新潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才穿那身衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}降落到地球之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角與地球人的少年命運般的邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}台詞全部即興完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剩下的交給導演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是亂來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那誰演地球人的少年啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我得顧著攝影機 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那只能是我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得很合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定很合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是打算在後台幫手的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要會臨機應變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對 拍攝現場可是活的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說得很懂似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼不行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和貴月學姐這麼漂亮的人演對手戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定會成為一生難忘的回憶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的人生到這就走到頂點了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這…一副樂在其中的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才沒這回事~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要演外星人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒…什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…那就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這裡就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開發等級F的邊境行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由於這顆星球對宇宙開發才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}載人登陸的…只有被稱作月球的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這顆星球的衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這台詞…挺真實的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然有點結結巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來 石垣同學上鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我是因為一些緣由而來到這個星球的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找…找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變成已經見過的設定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直在注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事實上是外星人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後我是黑衣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(722,660)}Men in black
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}黑…黑衣人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 石垣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 一不小心就太起勁兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}演對手戲的…死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣…好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…即興演得真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知不覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…現在是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為電影的內容改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在等檸檬學姐改劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是女主角展開逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後和黑衣人之間激烈的追逐戰啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡…怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這前面還有池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 學姐你上次不是提到過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有樹有池塘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是個沒什麼特別之處的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那該怎樣找呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也對呢 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是想去那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我挑選了一些相似的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但好像不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我還會再找的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這…你這…你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 把飲料拿給一夏學姐他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我之前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 你是不是知道我的心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有目共睹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼時候開始…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在支持我麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}交到女朋友要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會支持你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這恐怕…不太可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很痛啊 北原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一時發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再次開始拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了逃脫追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角回到了宇宙船上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那裡和伙伴會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰來演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這孩子的設定是宇宙船的生體終端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請多關照了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐 準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都搞不清楚誰才是導演了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}攝像機 準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 有追兵趕來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想都別想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥的仇就由我來報!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 石垣同學 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你幹嘛擅自跑進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼 這或許是演員的自我修養吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你修養太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…接下來要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從現在開始想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有住的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要來我家住嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一個人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家裡有很多空房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:10:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 真的十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終於回到主線了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 我怎麼就成演員了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而不是攝影師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還能和一夏學姐演對手戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這傢伙 難道說是故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變成和海人演對手戲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到頭來還是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你覺得今後 那兩個人會有什麼發展？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 學姐覺得怎麼發展好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…我覺得只要能幸福就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到頭來 導演和攝影師都由檸檬學姐包下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思我先去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這澡洗的真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 明天也要拍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然都看檸檬學姐安排
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐吩咐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要盡可能多拍一些女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}漸漸融入地球生活的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種場景就別拍進去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是在說電影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人如果知道了女主角的真實身份會怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那該由檸檬學姐去想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只會單純覺得「好厲害啊」這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是說那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「能不能把我也帶去宇宙呢」什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有規定限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你覺得和不同星球的人在一起也沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 只要不會射出什麼奇怪的液體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才沒那種東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也沒什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是不會在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 谷川家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 美櫻 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然今天不拍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟下著這麼大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到時再聯繫咯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在聊什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐 已經習慣這裡的生活了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 已經相當習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是啊 學姐有時挺怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然做出巧克力味的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算是吧 略顯微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 得去買菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 回去時繞路去趟超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說起來 紙巾也快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}洗滌劑也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那也順便去趟藥店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請問是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}午安 媽媽叫我拿過來給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}蕪菁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 有這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這房子很舊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等放晴了我去屋頂看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 這種事不多見嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請便請便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃 這話也不該由我來說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 不介意的話 一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 柑菜 出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明下著這麼大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是啊 還拎走了咱家裡的蕪菁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我女兒真是個奇怪的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 等她回來請告訴她我打過電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那就先這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}夾蕪菁的…三明治？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得嘛 就用這個試著做了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼地方搞錯了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然有點像烤餡餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.83,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}把麵團擀成薄皮 包入豆沙或蔬菜餡 在鐵板上烤製的食品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連葡萄柚蓋飯我都克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經沒什麼能阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請不要那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又在拍嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為說要我多拍點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自然的聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你說要「自然」也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學有兄弟姐妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是獨生子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…從小就常和哲朗一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒沒覺得寂寞什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你和石垣同學認識這麼久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他就像個傻弟弟一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我倒是覺得石垣同學更像哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是因為他個子高你才這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那學姐有沒有兄弟姐妹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有姐姐還有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來是三姐妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們家屬於女生多的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以到這裡來感覺挺新鮮的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來家裡有個男生…是這種感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果把海人比作家人 那像是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像是弟弟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…是有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過海人有時候也挺可靠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼說呢…說不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…聽不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是…剛才那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐是來這裡留學的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那打算在這兒待多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是半年呢…還是一年？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說了這種多餘的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯嗯 沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會出說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣多惹人厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不像樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不可愛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是美櫻說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去海人家了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這不是挺有勇氣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是沒去就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能融進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}心裡就像是有疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他們只是說話我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我討厭這麼想的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去告白咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海啊…還沒和學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果被拒絕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定會很尷尬的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是因為這樣而不愉快…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來大家還要一起拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是變成那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我怎麼還能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也一定會很受困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就這樣什麼也不做的 繼續煩惱下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你沒喜歡上誰就根本不知道我的感受！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎 你根本不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也說得太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}停了停了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會和往常一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起開開心心的拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍好了以後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在校園文化節之類上放…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會做回平常那個谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 走吧 哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個時候…發生了那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都不曾去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論是谷川的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是哲郎的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有北原的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都不曾去知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我被某個想法牽絆著…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…學姐終會消失的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拉我進去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我胳膊快沒勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}生命反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼晚來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說你給我從玄關進來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說吧 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川她今天來我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:22:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡……霧島海人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是沖繩啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很刺激啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 很誘人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 真受不了啊！
